entries.femaleVariant: You know nobody likes you, right?
Yep. Screw you too. Still want you at Arasaka.
I said I'm not interested. Besides, I prefer to work with people I actually respect.
All right, I'll name your price. Sending it your way now. That's your monthly take-home.
Holy shit... All right, you have my respect and admiration. When do I start?
